{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.1","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 19:1","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.018.033,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.019.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">David retourne \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-8: cf. 2 S 18:5, 31-33. J\u00e9 31:15. Ec 3:4.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.19.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>On vint dire \u00e0 Joab: Voici, le roi pleure et se lamente \u00e0 cause d\u2019Absalom.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19","name":"2 Samuel 19","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19.2","name":"2 Samuel 19:2","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18.33","name":"2 Samuel 18:33","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.33"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.2","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 19:2","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.019.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.019.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.19.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Et la victoire, ce jour-l\u00e0, fut chang\u00e9e en deuil pour tout le peuple, car en ce jour le peuple entendait dire: Le roi est afflig\u00e9 \u00e0 cause de son fils.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19","name":"2 Samuel 19","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19.3","name":"2 Samuel 19:3","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19.1","name":"2 Samuel 19:1","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.3","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 19:3","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.019.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.019.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.19.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Ce m\u00eame jour, le peuple rentra dans la ville \u00e0 la d\u00e9rob\u00e9e, comme l\u2019auraient fait des gens honteux d\u2019avoir pris la fuite dans le combat.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19","name":"2 Samuel 19","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19.4","name":"2 Samuel 19:4","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19.2","name":"2 Samuel 19:2","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.4","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 19:4","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.019.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.019.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.19.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Le roi s\u2019\u00e9tait couvert le visage, et il criait \u00e0 haute voix: Mon fils Absalom! Absalom, mon fils, mon fils!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19","name":"2 Samuel 19","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19.5","name":"2 Samuel 19:5","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19.3","name":"2 Samuel 19:3","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.5","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 19:5","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.019.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.019.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.19.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Joab entra dans la chambre o\u00f9 \u00e9tait le roi, et dit: Tu couvres aujourd\u2019hui de confusion la face de tous tes serviteurs, qui ont aujourd\u2019hui sauv\u00e9 ta vie, celle de tes fils et de tes filles, celle de tes femmes et de tes concubines.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19","name":"2 Samuel 19","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19.6","name":"2 Samuel 19:6","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19.4","name":"2 Samuel 19:4","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.6","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 19:6","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.019.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.019.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.19.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Tu aimes ceux qui te ha\u00efssent et tu hais ceux qui t\u2019aiment, car tu montres aujourd\u2019hui qu\u2019il n\u2019y a pour toi ni chefs ni serviteurs; et je vois maintenant que, si Absalom vivait et que nous fussions tous morts en ce jour, cela serait agr\u00e9able \u00e0 tes yeux.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19","name":"2 Samuel 19","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19.7","name":"2 Samuel 19:7","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19.5","name":"2 Samuel 19:5","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.7","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 19:7","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.019.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.019.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.19.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>L\u00e8ve-toi donc, sors, et parle au c\u0153ur de tes serviteurs! Car je jure par l\u2019\u00c9ternel que, si tu ne sors pas, il ne restera pas un homme avec toi cette nuit; et ce sera pour toi pire que tous les malheurs qui te sont arriv\u00e9s depuis ta jeunesse jusqu\u2019\u00e0 pr\u00e9sent.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19","name":"2 Samuel 19","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19.8","name":"2 Samuel 19:8","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19.6","name":"2 Samuel 19:6","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.8","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 19:8","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.019.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.019.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.19.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Alors le roi se leva, et il s\u2019assit \u00e0 la porte. On fit dire \u00e0 tout le peuple: Voici, le roi est assis \u00e0 la porte. Et tout le peuple vint devant le roi. Cependant Isra\u00ebl s\u2019\u00e9tait enfui, chacun dans sa tente.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19","name":"2 Samuel 19","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19.9","name":"2 Samuel 19:9","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19.7","name":"2 Samuel 19:7","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.9","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 19:9","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.019.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.019.010,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 9-15: cf. (2 S 15:13; 20:1, 2.) Ps 30:6.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.19.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Et dans toutes les tribus d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, tout le peuple \u00e9tait en contestation, disant: Le roi nous a d\u00e9livr\u00e9s de la main de nos ennemis, c\u2019est lui qui nous a sauv\u00e9s de la main des Philistins; et maintenant il a d\u00fb fuir du pays devant Absalom.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19","name":"2 Samuel 19","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19.10","name":"2 Samuel 19:10","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19.8","name":"2 Samuel 19:8","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.10","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 19:10","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.019.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.019.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.19.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Or Absalom, que nous avions oint pour qu\u2019il r\u00e9gn\u00e2t sur nous, est mort dans la bataille: pourquoi ne parlez-vous pas de faire revenir le roi?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19","name":"2 Samuel 19","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19.11","name":"2 Samuel 19:11","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19.9","name":"2 Samuel 19:9","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.11","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 19:11","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.019.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.019.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.19.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>De son c\u00f4t\u00e9, le roi David envoya dire aux sacrificateurs Tsadok et Abiathar: Parlez aux anciens de Juda, et dites-leur: Pourquoi seriez-vous les derniers \u00e0 ramener le roi dans sa maison? Car ce qui se disait dans tout Isra\u00ebl \u00e9tait parvenu jusqu\u2019au roi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19","name":"2 Samuel 19","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19.12","name":"2 Samuel 19:12","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19.10","name":"2 Samuel 19:10","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.12","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 19:12","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.019.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.019.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.19.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Vous \u00eates mes fr\u00e8res, vous \u00eates mes os et ma chair; pourquoi seriez-vous les derniers \u00e0 ramener le roi?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19","name":"2 Samuel 19","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19.13","name":"2 Samuel 19:13","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19.11","name":"2 Samuel 19:11","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.13","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 19:13","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.019.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.019.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.19.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Vous direz aussi \u00e0 Amasa: N\u2019es-tu pas mon os et ma chair? Que Dieu me traite dans toute sa rigueur, si tu ne deviens pas devant moi pour toujours chef de l\u2019arm\u00e9e \u00e0 la place de Joab!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19","name":"2 Samuel 19","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19.14","name":"2 Samuel 19:14","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19.12","name":"2 Samuel 19:12","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.14","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 19:14","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.019.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.019.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.19.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>David fl\u00e9chit le c\u0153ur de tous ceux de Juda, comme s\u2019ils n\u2019eussent \u00e9t\u00e9 qu\u2019un seul homme; et ils envoy\u00e8rent dire au roi: Reviens, toi, et tous tes serviteurs.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19","name":"2 Samuel 19","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19.15","name":"2 Samuel 19:15","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19.13","name":"2 Samuel 19:13","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.15","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 19:15","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.019.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.019.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.19.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Le roi revint et arriva jusqu\u2019au Jourdain; et Juda se rendit \u00e0 Guilgal, afin d\u2019aller \u00e0 la rencontre du roi et de lui faire passer le Jourdain.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19","name":"2 Samuel 19","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19.16","name":"2 Samuel 19:16","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19.14","name":"2 Samuel 19:14","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.16","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 19:16","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.019.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.019.017,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 16-23: cf. (2 S 16:5-13. 1 R 2:8, 9, 36-46.) \u00c9s 55:7.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.19.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>\n    Schime\u00ef, fils de Gu\u00e9ra, Benjamite, qui \u00e9tait de Bachurim, se h\u00e2ta de descendre avec ceux de Juda \u00e0 la rencontre du roi David.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19","name":"2 Samuel 19","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19.17","name":"2 Samuel 19:17","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19.15","name":"2 Samuel 19:15","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.17","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 19:17","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.019.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.019.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.19.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>Il avait avec lui mille hommes de Benjamin, et Tsiba, serviteur de la maison de Sa\u00fcl, et les quinze fils et les vingt serviteurs de Tsiba. Ils pass\u00e8rent le Jourdain \u00e0 la vue du roi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19","name":"2 Samuel 19","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19.18","name":"2 Samuel 19:18","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19.16","name":"2 Samuel 19:16","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.18","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 19:18","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.019.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.019.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.19.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>Le bateau, mis \u00e0 la disposition du roi, faisait la travers\u00e9e pour transporter sa maison; et au moment o\u00f9 le roi allait passer le Jourdain, Schime\u00ef, fils de Gu\u00e9ra, se prosterna devant lui.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19","name":"2 Samuel 19","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19.19","name":"2 Samuel 19:19","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19.17","name":"2 Samuel 19:17","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.19","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 19:19","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.019.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.019.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.19.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>Et il dit au roi: Que mon seigneur ne tienne pas compte de mon iniquit\u00e9, qu\u2019il oublie que ton serviteur l\u2019a offens\u00e9 le jour o\u00f9 le roi mon seigneur sortait de J\u00e9rusalem, et que le roi n\u2019y ait point \u00e9gard!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19","name":"2 Samuel 19","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19.20","name":"2 Samuel 19:20","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19.18","name":"2 Samuel 19:18","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.20","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 19:20","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.019.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.019.021,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.19.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>Car ton serviteur reconna\u00eet qu\u2019il a p\u00e9ch\u00e9. Et voici, je viens aujourd\u2019hui le premier de toute la maison de Joseph \u00e0 la rencontre du roi mon seigneur.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19","name":"2 Samuel 19","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19.21","name":"2 Samuel 19:21","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19.19","name":"2 Samuel 19:19","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.21","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 19:21","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.019.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.019.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.19.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup>Alors Abischa\u00ef, fils de Tseruja, prit la parole et dit: Schime\u00ef ne doit-il pas mourir pour avoir maudit l\u2019oint de l\u2019\u00c9ternel?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19","name":"2 Samuel 19","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19.22","name":"2 Samuel 19:22","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19.20","name":"2 Samuel 19:20","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.22","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 19:22","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.019.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.019.023,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.19.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>Mais David dit: Qu\u2019ai-je affaire avec vous, fils de Tseruja, et pourquoi vous montrez-vous aujourd\u2019hui mes adversaires? Aujourd\u2019hui ferait-on mourir un homme en Isra\u00ebl? Ne sais-je donc pas que je r\u00e8gne aujourd\u2019hui sur Isra\u00ebl?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19","name":"2 Samuel 19","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19.23","name":"2 Samuel 19:23","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19.21","name":"2 Samuel 19:21","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.23","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 19:23","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.019.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.019.024,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.19.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup>Et le roi dit \u00e0 Schime\u00ef: Tu ne mourras point! Et le roi le lui jura.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19","name":"2 Samuel 19","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19.24","name":"2 Samuel 19:24","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.24"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19.22","name":"2 Samuel 19:22","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"24","lastverse":"24","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.24","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.24","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 19:24","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.019.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.019.025,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 24-30: cf. 2 S 16:1-4. Ps 37:6.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.19.24\" class=\"v\">24<\/sup>Mephiboscheth, fils de Sa\u00fcl, descendit aussi \u00e0 la rencontre du roi. Il n\u2019avait point soign\u00e9 ses pieds, ni fait sa barbe, ni lav\u00e9 ses v\u00eatements, depuis le jour o\u00f9 le roi s\u2019en \u00e9tait all\u00e9 jusqu\u2019\u00e0 celui o\u00f9 il revenait en paix.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19","name":"2 Samuel 19","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19.25","name":"2 Samuel 19:25","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.25"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19.23","name":"2 Samuel 19:23","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"25","lastverse":"25","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.25","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.25","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 19:25","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.019.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.019.026,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.19.25\" class=\"v\">25<\/sup>Lorsqu\u2019il se rendit au-devant du roi \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem, le roi lui dit: Pourquoi n\u2019es-tu pas venu avec moi, Mephiboscheth?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19","name":"2 Samuel 19","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19.26","name":"2 Samuel 19:26","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.26"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19.24","name":"2 Samuel 19:24","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"26","lastverse":"26","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.26","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.26","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 19:26","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.019.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.019.027,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.19.26\" class=\"v\">26<\/sup>Et il r\u00e9pondit: O roi mon seigneur, mon serviteur m\u2019a tromp\u00e9, car ton serviteur, qui est boiteux, avait dit: Je ferai seller mon \u00e2ne, je le monterai, et j\u2019irai avec le roi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19","name":"2 Samuel 19","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19.27","name":"2 Samuel 19:27","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.27"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19.25","name":"2 Samuel 19:25","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"27","lastverse":"27","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.27","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.27","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 19:27","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.019.026,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.019.028,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.19.27\" class=\"v\">27<\/sup>Et il a calomni\u00e9 ton serviteur aupr\u00e8s de mon seigneur le roi. Mais mon seigneur le roi est comme un ange de Dieu. Fais ce qui te semblera bon.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19","name":"2 Samuel 19","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19.28","name":"2 Samuel 19:28","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.28"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19.26","name":"2 Samuel 19:26","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.26"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"28","lastverse":"28","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.28","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.28","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 19:28","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.019.027,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.019.029,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.19.28\" class=\"v\">28<\/sup>Car tous ceux de la maison de mon p\u00e8re n\u2019ont \u00e9t\u00e9 que des gens dignes de mort devant le roi mon seigneur; et cependant tu as mis ton serviteur au nombre de ceux qui mangent \u00e0 ta table. Quel droit puis-je encore avoir, et qu\u2019ai-je \u00e0 demander au roi?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19","name":"2 Samuel 19","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19.29","name":"2 Samuel 19:29","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.29"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19.27","name":"2 Samuel 19:27","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.27"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"29","lastverse":"29","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.29","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.29","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 19:29","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.019.028,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.019.030,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.19.29\" class=\"v\">29<\/sup>Le roi lui dit: A quoi bon toutes tes paroles? Je l\u2019ai d\u00e9clar\u00e9: Toi et Tsiba, vous partagerez les terres.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19","name":"2 Samuel 19","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19.30","name":"2 Samuel 19:30","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.30"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19.28","name":"2 Samuel 19:28","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.28"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"30","lastverse":"30","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.30","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.30","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 19:30","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.019.029,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.019.031,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.19.30\" class=\"v\">30<\/sup>Et Mephiboscheth dit au roi: Qu\u2019il prenne m\u00eame le tout, puisque le roi mon seigneur rentre en paix dans sa maison.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19","name":"2 Samuel 19","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19.31","name":"2 Samuel 19:31","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.31"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19.29","name":"2 Samuel 19:29","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.29"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"31","lastverse":"31","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.31","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.31","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 19:31","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.019.030,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.019.032,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 31-43: cf. (2 S 17:27-29. 1 R 2:7.) 2 S 20:1, etc. Mt 10:41, 42; 25:34-40.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.19.31\" class=\"v\">31<\/sup>Barzilla\u00ef, le Galaadite, descendit de Roguelim, et passa le Jourdain avec le roi, pour l\u2019accompagner jusqu\u2019au-del\u00e0 du Jourdain.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19","name":"2 Samuel 19","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19.32","name":"2 Samuel 19:32","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.32"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19.30","name":"2 Samuel 19:30","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.30"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"32","lastverse":"32","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.32","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.32","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 19:32","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.019.031,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.019.033,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.19.32\" class=\"v\">32<\/sup>Barzilla\u00ef \u00e9tait tr\u00e8s vieux, \u00e2g\u00e9 de quatre-vingts ans. Il avait entretenu le roi pendant son s\u00e9jour \u00e0 Mahana\u00efm, car c\u2019\u00e9tait un homme fort riche.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19","name":"2 Samuel 19","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19.33","name":"2 Samuel 19:33","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.33"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19.31","name":"2 Samuel 19:31","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.31"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"33","lastverse":"33","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.33","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.33","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 19:33","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.019.032,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.019.034,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.19.33\" class=\"v\">33<\/sup>Le roi dit \u00e0 Barzilla\u00ef: Viens avec moi, je te nourrirai chez moi \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19","name":"2 Samuel 19","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19.34","name":"2 Samuel 19:34","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.34"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19.32","name":"2 Samuel 19:32","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.32"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"34","lastverse":"34","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.34","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.34","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 19:34","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.019.033,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.019.035,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.19.34\" class=\"v\">34<\/sup>Mais Barzilla\u00ef r\u00e9pondit au roi: Combien d\u2019ann\u00e9es vivrai-je encore, pour que je monte avec le roi \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19","name":"2 Samuel 19","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19.35","name":"2 Samuel 19:35","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.35"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19.33","name":"2 Samuel 19:33","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.33"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"35","lastverse":"35","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.35","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.35","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 19:35","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.019.034,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.019.036,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.19.35\" class=\"v\">35<\/sup>Je suis aujourd\u2019hui \u00e2g\u00e9 de quatre-vingts ans. Puis-je conna\u00eetre ce qui est bon et ce qui est mauvais? Ton serviteur peut-il savourer ce qu\u2019il mange et ce qu\u2019il boit? Puis-je encore entendre la voix des chanteurs et des chanteuses? Et pourquoi ton serviteur serait-il encore \u00e0 charge \u00e0 mon seigneur le roi?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19","name":"2 Samuel 19","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19.36","name":"2 Samuel 19:36","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.36"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19.34","name":"2 Samuel 19:34","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.34"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"36","lastverse":"36","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.36","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.36","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 19:36","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.019.035,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.019.037,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.19.36\" class=\"v\">36<\/sup>Ton serviteur ira un peu au-del\u00e0 du Jourdain avec le roi. Pourquoi, d\u2019ailleurs, le roi m\u2019accorderait-il ce bienfait?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19","name":"2 Samuel 19","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19.37","name":"2 Samuel 19:37","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.37"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19.35","name":"2 Samuel 19:35","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.35"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"37","lastverse":"37","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.37","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.37","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 19:37","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.019.036,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.019.038,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.19.37\" class=\"v\">37<\/sup>Que ton serviteur s\u2019en retourne, et que je meure dans ma ville, pr\u00e8s du s\u00e9pulcre de mon p\u00e8re et de ma m\u00e8re! Mais voici ton serviteur Kimham, qui passera avec le roi mon seigneur; fais pour lui ce que tu trouveras bon.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19","name":"2 Samuel 19","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19.38","name":"2 Samuel 19:38","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.38"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19.36","name":"2 Samuel 19:36","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.36"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"38","lastverse":"38","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.38","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.38","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 19:38","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.019.037,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.019.039,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.19.38\" class=\"v\">38<\/sup>Le roi dit: Que Kimham passe avec moi, et je ferai pour lui ce qui te plaira; tout ce que tu d\u00e9sireras de moi, je te l\u2019accorderai.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19","name":"2 Samuel 19","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19.39","name":"2 Samuel 19:39","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.39"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19.37","name":"2 Samuel 19:37","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.37"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"39","lastverse":"39","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.39","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.39","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 19:39","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.019.038,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.019.040,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.19.39\" class=\"v\">39<\/sup>Quand tout le peuple eut pass\u00e9 le Jourdain et que le roi l\u2019eut aussi pass\u00e9, le roi baisa Barzilla\u00ef et le b\u00e9nit. Et Barzilla\u00ef retourna dans sa demeure.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19","name":"2 Samuel 19","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19.40","name":"2 Samuel 19:40","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.40"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19.38","name":"2 Samuel 19:38","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.38"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"40","lastverse":"40","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.40","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.40","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 19:40","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.019.039,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.019.041,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.19.40\" class=\"v\">40<\/sup>Le roi se dirigea vers Guilgal, et Kimham l\u2019accompagna. Tout le peuple de Juda et la moiti\u00e9 du peuple d\u2019Isra\u00ebl avaient fait passer le Jourdain au roi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19","name":"2 Samuel 19","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19.41","name":"2 Samuel 19:41","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.41"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19.39","name":"2 Samuel 19:39","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.39"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"41","lastverse":"41","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.41","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.41","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 19:41","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.019.040,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.019.042,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.19.41\" class=\"v\">41<\/sup>Mais voici, tous les hommes d\u2019Isra\u00ebl abord\u00e8rent le roi, et lui dirent: Pourquoi nos fr\u00e8res, les hommes de Juda, t\u2019ont-ils enlev\u00e9, et ont-ils fait passer le Jourdain au roi, \u00e0 sa maison, et \u00e0 tous les gens de David?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19","name":"2 Samuel 19","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19.42","name":"2 Samuel 19:42","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.42"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19.40","name":"2 Samuel 19:40","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.40"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"42","lastverse":"42","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.42","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.42","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 19:42","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.019.041,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.019.043,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.19.42\" class=\"v\">42<\/sup>Tous les hommes de Juda r\u00e9pondirent aux hommes d\u2019Isra\u00ebl: C\u2019est que le roi nous tient de plus pr\u00e8s; et qu\u2019y a-t-il l\u00e0 pour vous irriter? Avons-nous v\u00e9cu aux d\u00e9pens du roi? Nous a-t-il fait des pr\u00e9sents?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19","name":"2 Samuel 19","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19.43","name":"2 Samuel 19:43","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.43"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19.41","name":"2 Samuel 19:41","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.41"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"43","lastverse":"43","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.43","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.43","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 19:43","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.019.042,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.020.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.19.43\" class=\"v\">43<\/sup>Et les hommes d\u2019Isra\u00ebl r\u00e9pondirent aux hommes de Juda: Le roi nous appartient dix fois autant, et David m\u00eame plus qu\u2019\u00e0 vous. Pourquoi nous avez-vous m\u00e9pris\u00e9s? N\u2019avons-nous pas \u00e9t\u00e9 les premiers \u00e0 proposer de faire revenir notre roi? Et les hommes de Juda parl\u00e8rent avec plus de violence que les hommes d\u2019Isra\u00ebl.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19","name":"2 Samuel 19","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.20.1","name":"2 Samuel 20:1","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19.42","name":"2 Samuel 19:42","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.42"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fb8711071.15860317');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb8711071.15860317\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fb8711071.15860317","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fb8711071.15860317'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb8711071.15860317\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}